<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:31.641 --> 04:32.551
What?

04:34.261 --> 04:36.473
Caleb decided to move on.

04:37.431 --> 04:39.340
He said he didn't think it'd
be good for him to live here,

04:39.341 --> 04:41.061
even though he'd love to be near us.

04:42.221 --> 04:43.423
(SCOFFS)

04:46.923 --> 04:49.721
Oh, well, at least he
left a note this time.

04:55.261 --> 04:57.099
Yeah, I talked to him.

04:58.267 --> 04:59.675
What did you say?

04:59.676 --> 05:02.165
Basically the stuff
that we talked about...

05:02.682 --> 05:05.577
how much pressure it would put
on your relationship with Katie.

05:08.658 --> 05:12.590
He knows you love him, and
he... he gets it, Dylan.

05:12.591 --> 05:14.340
(SCOFFS)

05:14.341 --> 05:16.471
I feel terrible...

05:20.011 --> 05:21.799
And relieved.

05:23.261 --> 05:25.380
And... and I feel terrible
that I feel relieved.

05:25.381 --> 05:27.840
- I mean...
- Hey, it's not your fault.

05:27.841 --> 05:29.300
You can't fix something that happened

05:29.301 --> 05:30.970
before you were born.

05:30.971 --> 05:32.590
And you've done the best you
possibly could with it.

05:32.591 --> 05:33.511
It's...

05:35.881 --> 05:38.057
We're trying to live a
life in the sun here.

05:38.591 --> 05:40.089
No secrets.

05:40.681 --> 05:44.341
It's a good path. Let's
just try and stay on it.

05:46.431 --> 05:47.761
Okay.

05:50.575 --> 05:51.550
God, I know how hard it is.

05:51.551 --> 05:53.522
I feel the same way about my mom.

05:54.301 --> 05:57.300
I wish Katie could know
her and... and Caleb,

05:57.301 --> 06:00.380
but I-I just don't think it's
in anyone's best interest.

06:00.381 --> 06:02.010
Katie will be short on grandparents,

06:02.011 --> 06:05.260
but at least she'll live
in a honest, open world...

06:05.261 --> 06:06.550
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:06.551 --> 06:08.800
Especially between us.

06:08.801 --> 06:10.590
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:10.591 --> 06:11.640
I hope so.

06:11.641 --> 06:18.640
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:18.641 --> 06:21.590
