10:26.534 --> 10:28.663
<i>♪ Don't know about a science book ♪</i>

10:28.664 --> 10:29.894
Norman?

10:29.895 --> 10:31.839
<i>♪ Don't know much about
the French I took ♪</i>

10:31.840 --> 10:32.815
Yes?

10:32.816 --> 10:34.724
If you're Norman, your
coffee's sitting here.

10:34.725 --> 10:36.314
<i>♪ But I do know that I love you ♪</i>

10:36.315 --> 10:39.442
- Sorry. Thanks.
- No problem.

